OL,3,CSomerset mother continues to search
OL,4,Cfor son who vanished in Sardinia a
OL,5,Cyear ago
OL,7,FThe mother of a Somerset man who
OL,8,Fvanished in Sardinia six months ago
OL,9,Fhas spoken of her torment as the
OL,10,Fsearch for her son continues on year
OL,11,Fsince he was last seen.
OL,13,FCristina Pittalis from Chard is
OL,14,Fdesperately seeking answers about the
OL,15,Fdisappearance of her 25-year-old son
OL,16,FMichael Frison, who went missing
OL,17,Fwhilst visiting the Italian island in
OL,18,FJuly 2024.
