OL,3,CSomerset mother continues to search
OL,4,Cfor son who vanished in Sardinia a
OL,5,Cyear ago
OL,7,FMichael had travelled to Sardinia to
OL,8,Fvisit his grandparents and journeyed
OL,9,Fto the remote Luras region on 12th
OL,10,FJuly.
OL,12,FThe following day, he set off for a
OL,13,Fwalk and has not been seen since.
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country,
OL,16,FCristina said it's her "mission in
OL,17,Flife" to find her son.
