OL,3,CSomerset mother continues to search
OL,4,Cfor son who vanished in Sardinia a
OL,5,Cyear ago
OL,7,FThe official search operation, which
OL,8,Finvolved drones, a helicopter,
OL,9,Fmountain rescue teams and volunteers,
OL,10,Fwas called off after 10 days.
OL,12,FSince then, Cristina has taken it upon
OL,13,Fherself to continue searching for
OL,14,FMichael alongside family and friends -
OL,15,Fand has since moved to Sardinia.
OL,17,FWhilst in Sardinia, Michael met up
OL,18,Fwith a friend he had encountered
OL,19,Fonline, known as Niomi.
