OL,3,CSomerset mother continues to search
OL,4,Cfor son who vanished in Sardinia a
OL,5,Cyear ago
OL,7,FShe assisted Italian authorities with
OL,8,Ftheir initial search and investigation
OL,9,Fbut has since left the island - ITV
OL,10,FWest Country has been unable to speak
OL,11,Fto Niomi.
OL,13,FCristina is particularly keen to speak
OL,14,Fwith Niomi again, believing she may
OL,15,Fhold crucial information that could
OL,16,Fhelp locate her son.
OL,18,F"We need to find Michael's friend, I'm
OL,19,Fsure she holds vital information, she
OL,20,Fwas the last person who saw him,"
OL,21,FCristina explained.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
