OL,3,CSomerset mother continues to search
OL,4,Cfor son who vanished in Sardinia a
OL,5,Cyear ago
OL,7,FShe is urging UK authorities to help
OL,8,Fwith the search efforts, as she
OL,9,Fbelieves Michael's disappearance is
OL,10,Flinked to a online community he had
OL,11,Fmet when he was in the UK.
OL,13,FShe went on to speak of the impact
OL,14,FMichael's disappearance has had on
OL,15,Fher, "some days it's hard to find the
OL,16,Fstrength to carry on, but it's our
OL,17,Flove, our family which gives me the
OL,18,Fstrength to continue."
